formatted_address: 283 Bukit Batok East Ave 3, #01-285 Block 283, Singapore 650283
name: Hao Xiang Mixed Veg Rice

reviews.text: Family member ordered this takeaway. On one side, the fish was normal. Flipped to the other side, whole side was burnt and chao tah. Suspect they put up the normal side for takeaway and covered the ‘bad’ side. I think it was bad ethics and they shouldn’t have kept the fish if it was burnt.
Family member ordered two veg dishes and they cost $4, it's confirm a jacked up price. And the bitter gourd was really not fresh, so got scammed

Relatively new stall in the coffeeshop. The selection quite good but quality hit and miss, eg. the prawn fritters looked and tasted overnight as there were so much oil retention in the batter, possibly due to 2nd frying. But for such comprehensive selections, you do not expect every dish to be on point.

vicinity: 283 Bukit Batok East Avenue 3, #01-285 Block 283, Singapore
